{"title":"Polygon Mesh Processing Notes","date":"2024-10-04T03:38:40.000Z","toc":true,"summary":"Polygon Mesh Processing 读书笔记","source":"_posts/Polygon-Mesh-Processing-Notes.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Polygon Mesh Processing Notes\ndate: 2024-10-04 11:38:40\ntags: Graphics\ntoc: true\nsummary: \"Polygon Mesh Processing 读书笔记\"\n---\n\n# 1. Surface Representations\n\n曲面主要有两种表示方法：\n\n1. 参数表示 (Parametric Representations)\n\n   参数表示使用参数化函数来描述曲面。定义参数域 $\\Omega \\subset \\mathbf{R^2}$，曲面 $S = f(\\Omega) \\subset \\mathbf{R^3}$，参数化函数 $f: \\Omega \\rightarrow S$ 将参数域映射到曲面。\n\n   如单位圆的参数化函数：\n   $$\n   f(t) = (\\cos(t), \\sin(t)) \\ \\ \\ \\ t \\in [0, 2\\pi]\n   $$\n\n2. 隐式表示 (Implicit Representations)\n\n   隐式表示通过一个标量函数的零集来表示，即所使函数值为 0 的点构成了曲面。定义三维空间 $\\mathbf{R}^3$，$\\mathbf{x}$ 为 $\\mathbf{R}^3$ 中一点。函数 $F: \\mathbf{R}^3 \\rightarrow \\mathbf{R}$，曲面 $S$ 定义为 $F$ 的零集，即 $S = \\{\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbf{R}^3 | F(\\mathbf{x}) = 0\\}$\n\n   如单位圆的隐式表示：\n   $$\n   F(x, y) = \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} - 1 = 0\n   $$\n\n对于复杂形体，通常难以用单一函数精确表示。于是，通常会将函数域划分为若干个子域，对每个部分的形体使用独立的函数来描述。\n\n参数表示法和隐式表示法各有所长，常见的曲面几何操作可以分为以下三类：\n\n1. Evaluation（评估）\n\n   主要是对于曲面属性进行采样，如表面法线场。典型的应用场景是曲面渲染，需要评估法线来决定光照效果。\n\n2. Query（查询）\n\n   查询给定一点和曲面的空间关系或者计算点到曲面的距离。例如在碰撞检测中需要知道点在曲面围成的空间的内部或者外部。\n\n3. Modification（修改）\n\n   曲面可以通过几何或者拓扑上的变换来进行修改。前者指表面形状的变形，后者指表面结构的修改（例如合并、切割或者删除表面的一部分）\n\n## 1. Surface Definition and Properties\n\n曲面的通常定义为：“嵌入三维空间 $\\mathbf{R}^3$ 中可定向的连续二维流形”。直观地理解，它可以看作是非退化三维实体的边界面，其中“非退化”意味着这个实体没有无限薄的部分或特征，这样曲面就可以正确地实体的“内部”和“外部”分开。\n\n- **二维流形(manifold)：**指的是每个点的局部邻域内可以看作是一个二维的平面\n\n- **可定向(orientable)：**指的是在曲面的每一点都可以选择一个一致的法线方向（例如，全部朝向内部或全部朝向外部），并且当在曲面上移动时，法线方向可以保持连续变化，而不会出现突然翻转或不一致\n\n  可定向的曲面比如像球面，圆环等。而像莫比乌斯带是不可定向的，沿着它走一圈时，初始定义的法线方向会发生翻转。\n\n- **非退化：**指的是曲面没有异常或退化的地方，比如没有无限薄的尖锐边缘或奇点，确保曲面将三维实体的内外分隔开。\n\n  比如一个圆锥的锥尖就是一个典型的退化点。\n\n曲面亦可分为带边界的曲面和不带边界的曲面。\n\n- 比如球面，环面这些曲面没有任何边界，封闭且连续\n\n- 比如圆盘（具有一个圆周作为边界）、矩形（四条边作为边界）。这些曲面存在边界点，但仍然是流形，因为在大多数点上局部结构类似于二维平面\n\n  带孔洞的曲面属于带边界的流形曲面，因为孔洞的边缘形成了曲面的边界\n\n曲面的建立很多时候是通过离散采样获得的。要将离散采样的数据转化为一个数学上可定义的曲面，需要保证曲面在采样点之间是连续的，才能在采样点之间插值出曲面结构。\n\n","slug":"Polygon-Mesh-Processing-Notes","published":true,"updated":"2024-10-27T14:53:06.836Z","_id":"cm2hd052n000k7ouf0gmd6ijj","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"html":"<h1>1. Surface Representations</h1>\n<p>曲面主要有两种表示方法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>参数表示 (Parametric Representations)</p>\n<p>参数表示使用参数化函数来描述曲面。定义参数域 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo>⊂</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn mathvariant=\"bold\">2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Omega \\subset \\mathbf{R^2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7224em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⊂</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathbf mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，曲面 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⊂</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn mathvariant=\"bold\">3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S = f(\\Omega) \\subset \\mathbf{R^3}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⊂</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathbf mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，参数化函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>:</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">f: \\Omega \\rightarrow S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 将参数域映射到曲面。</p>\n<p>如单位圆的参数化函数：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>    </mtext><mi>t</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">f(t) = (\\cos(t), \\sin(t)) \\ \\ \\ \\ t \\in [0, 2\\pi]\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mop\">cos</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">sin</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">))</span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>隐式表示 (Implicit Representations)</p>\n<p>隐式表示通过一个标量函数的零集来表示，即所使函数值为 0 的点构成了曲面。定义三维空间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{x}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span></span></span></span> 为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 中一点。函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo>:</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F: \\mathbf{R}^3 \\rightarrow \\mathbf{R}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span></span></span></span>，曲面 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 定义为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span></span></span></span> 的零集，即 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S = \\{\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbf{R}^3 | F(\\mathbf{x}) = 0\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0641em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>如单位圆的隐式表示：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(x, y) = \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} - 1 = 0\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.24em;vertical-align:-0.2333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.0067em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.2em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.2em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\" style=\"padding-left:1em;\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-2.9667em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.2em;\"></span><span class=\"hide-tail\" style=\"min-width:1.02em;height:1.28em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"400em\" height=\"1.28em\" viewBox=\"0 0 400000 1296\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin slice\"><path d=\"M263,681c0.7,0,18,39.7,52,119\nc34,79.3,68.167,158.7,102.5,238c34.3,79.3,51.8,119.3,52.5,120\nc340,-704.7,510.7,-1060.3,512,-1067\nl0 -0\nc4.7,-7.3,11,-11,19,-11\nH40000v40H1012.3\ns-271.3,567,-271.3,567c-38.7,80.7,-84,175,-136,283c-52,108,-89.167,185.3,-111.5,232\nc-22.3,46.7,-33.8,70.3,-34.5,71c-4.7,4.7,-12.3,7,-23,7s-12,-1,-12,-1\ns-109,-253,-109,-253c-72.7,-168,-109.3,-252,-110,-252c-10.7,8,-22,16.7,-34,26\nc-22,17.3,-33.3,26,-34,26s-26,-26,-26,-26s76,-59,76,-59s76,-60,76,-60z\nM1001 80h400000v40h-400000z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2333em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>对于复杂形体，通常难以用单一函数精确表示。于是，通常会将函数域划分为若干个子域，对每个部分的形体使用独立的函数来描述。</p>\n<p>参数表示法和隐式表示法各有所长，常见的曲面几何操作可以分为以下三类：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Evaluation（评估）</p>\n<p>主要是对于曲面属性进行采样，如表面法线场。典型的应用场景是曲面渲染，需要评估法线来决定光照效果。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Query（查询）</p>\n<p>查询给定一点和曲面的空间关系或者计算点到曲面的距离。例如在碰撞检测中需要知道点在曲面围成的空间的内部或者外部。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Modification（修改）</p>\n<p>曲面可以通过几何或者拓扑上的变换来进行修改。前者指表面形状的变形，后者指表面结构的修改（例如合并、切割或者删除表面的一部分）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"1-Surface-Definition-and-Properties\">1. Surface Definition and Properties</h2>\n<p>曲面的通常定义为：“嵌入三维空间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 中可定向的连续二维流形”。直观地理解，它可以看作是非退化三维实体的边界面，其中“非退化”意味着这个实体没有无限薄的部分或特征，这样曲面就可以正确地实体的“内部”和“外部”分开。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>**二维流形(manifold)：**指的是每个点的局部邻域内可以看作是一个二维的平面</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>**可定向(orientable)：**指的是在曲面的每一点都可以选择一个一致的法线方向（例如，全部朝向内部或全部朝向外部），并且当在曲面上移动时，法线方向可以保持连续变化，而不会出现突然翻转或不一致</p>\n<p>可定向的曲面比如像球面，圆环等。而像莫比乌斯带是不可定向的，沿着它走一圈时，初始定义的法线方向会发生翻转。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>**非退化：**指的是曲面没有异常或退化的地方，比如没有无限薄的尖锐边缘或奇点，确保曲面将三维实体的内外分隔开。</p>\n<p>比如一个圆锥的锥尖就是一个典型的退化点。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>曲面亦可分为带边界的曲面和不带边界的曲面。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>比如球面，环面这些曲面没有任何边界，封闭且连续</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>比如圆盘（具有一个圆周作为边界）、矩形（四条边作为边界）。这些曲面存在边界点，但仍然是流形，因为在大多数点上局部结构类似于二维平面</p>\n<p>带孔洞的曲面属于带边界的流形曲面，因为孔洞的边缘形成了曲面的边界</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>曲面的建立很多时候是通过离散采样获得的。要将离散采样的数据转化为一个数学上可定义的曲面，需要保证曲面在采样点之间是连续的，才能在采样点之间插值出曲面结构。</p>\n","excerpt":"","more":"<h1>1. Surface Representations</h1>\n<p>曲面主要有两种表示方法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>参数表示 (Parametric Representations)</p>\n<p>参数表示使用参数化函数来描述曲面。定义参数域 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo>⊂</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn mathvariant=\"bold\">2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Omega \\subset \\mathbf{R^2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7224em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⊂</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathbf mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，曲面 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⊂</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn mathvariant=\"bold\">3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S = f(\\Omega) \\subset \\mathbf{R^3}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">⊂</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathbf mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，参数化函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>:</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">f: \\Omega \\rightarrow S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 将参数域映射到曲面。</p>\n<p>如单位圆的参数化函数：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mtext>    </mtext><mi>t</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">f(t) = (\\cos(t), \\sin(t)) \\ \\ \\ \\ t \\in [0, 2\\pi]\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mop\">cos</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">sin</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">))</span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mspace\"> </span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">π</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>隐式表示 (Implicit Representations)</p>\n<p>隐式表示通过一个标量函数的零集来表示，即所使函数值为 0 的点构成了曲面。定义三维空间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{x}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span></span></span></span> 为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 中一点。函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo>:</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F: \\mathbf{R}^3 \\rightarrow \\mathbf{R}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span></span></span></span>，曲面 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 定义为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span></span></span></span> 的零集，即 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S = \\{\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbf{R}^3 | F(\\mathbf{x}) = 0\\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.0641em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathbf\">x</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>如单位圆的隐式表示：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(x, y) = \\sqrt{x^2 + y^2} - 1 = 0\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.24em;vertical-align:-0.2333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.0067em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.2em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.2em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\" style=\"padding-left:1em;\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-2.9667em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.2em;\"></span><span class=\"hide-tail\" style=\"min-width:1.02em;height:1.28em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"400em\" height=\"1.28em\" viewBox=\"0 0 400000 1296\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin slice\"><path d=\"M263,681c0.7,0,18,39.7,52,119\nc34,79.3,68.167,158.7,102.5,238c34.3,79.3,51.8,119.3,52.5,120\nc340,-704.7,510.7,-1060.3,512,-1067\nl0 -0\nc4.7,-7.3,11,-11,19,-11\nH40000v40H1012.3\ns-271.3,567,-271.3,567c-38.7,80.7,-84,175,-136,283c-52,108,-89.167,185.3,-111.5,232\nc-22.3,46.7,-33.8,70.3,-34.5,71c-4.7,4.7,-12.3,7,-23,7s-12,-1,-12,-1\ns-109,-253,-109,-253c-72.7,-168,-109.3,-252,-110,-252c-10.7,8,-22,16.7,-34,26\nc-22,17.3,-33.3,26,-34,26s-26,-26,-26,-26s76,-59,76,-59s76,-60,76,-60z\nM1001 80h400000v40h-400000z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2333em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>对于复杂形体，通常难以用单一函数精确表示。于是，通常会将函数域划分为若干个子域，对每个部分的形体使用独立的函数来描述。</p>\n<p>参数表示法和隐式表示法各有所长，常见的曲面几何操作可以分为以下三类：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Evaluation（评估）</p>\n<p>主要是对于曲面属性进行采样，如表面法线场。典型的应用场景是曲面渲染，需要评估法线来决定光照效果。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Query（查询）</p>\n<p>查询给定一点和曲面的空间关系或者计算点到曲面的距离。例如在碰撞检测中需要知道点在曲面围成的空间的内部或者外部。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Modification（修改）</p>\n<p>曲面可以通过几何或者拓扑上的变换来进行修改。前者指表面形状的变形，后者指表面结构的修改（例如合并、切割或者删除表面的一部分）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"1-Surface-Definition-and-Properties\">1. Surface Definition and Properties</h2>\n<p>曲面的通常定义为：“嵌入三维空间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">R</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathbf{R}^3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathbf\">R</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 中可定向的连续二维流形”。直观地理解，它可以看作是非退化三维实体的边界面，其中“非退化”意味着这个实体没有无限薄的部分或特征，这样曲面就可以正确地实体的“内部”和“外部”分开。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>**二维流形(manifold)：**指的是每个点的局部邻域内可以看作是一个二维的平面</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>**可定向(orientable)：**指的是在曲面的每一点都可以选择一个一致的法线方向（例如，全部朝向内部或全部朝向外部），并且当在曲面上移动时，法线方向可以保持连续变化，而不会出现突然翻转或不一致</p>\n<p>可定向的曲面比如像球面，圆环等。而像莫比乌斯带是不可定向的，沿着它走一圈时，初始定义的法线方向会发生翻转。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>**非退化：**指的是曲面没有异常或退化的地方，比如没有无限薄的尖锐边缘或奇点，确保曲面将三维实体的内外分隔开。</p>\n<p>比如一个圆锥的锥尖就是一个典型的退化点。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>曲面亦可分为带边界的曲面和不带边界的曲面。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>比如球面，环面这些曲面没有任何边界，封闭且连续</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>比如圆盘（具有一个圆周作为边界）、矩形（四条边作为边界）。这些曲面存在边界点，但仍然是流形，因为在大多数点上局部结构类似于二维平面</p>\n<p>带孔洞的曲面属于带边界的流形曲面，因为孔洞的边缘形成了曲面的边界</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>曲面的建立很多时候是通过离散采样获得的。要将离散采样的数据转化为一个数学上可定义的曲面，需要保证曲面在采样点之间是连续的，才能在采样点之间插值出曲面结构。</p>\n","path":"2024/10/04/Polygon-Mesh-Processing-Notes/","permalink":"https://zweireverberate.icu/2024/10/04/Polygon-Mesh-Processing-Notes/","tags":[{"name":"Graphics","_id":"cm2hd052n000m7oufbgrz49m9","slug":"Graphics","path":"tags/Graphics/","permalink":"https://zweireverberate.icu/tags/Graphics/","length":3}],"categories":[],"prev":{"title":"Shadertoy Notes","date":"2024-10-10T15:15:59.000Z","summary":"Shadertoy 笔记","slug":"Shadertoy-Notes","published":true,"updated":"2024-11-19T13:57:24.596Z","_id":"cm3oiv08x000278uf5htd6j44","layout":"post","photos":[],"excerpt":"","path":"2024/10/10/Shadertoy-Notes/","permalink":"https://zweireverberate.icu/2024/10/10/Shadertoy-Notes/","__post":true},"next":{"title":"Coding Problems","date":"2024-09-17T11:07:04.000Z","summary":"编程练习","slug":"Coding-Problems","published":true,"updated":"2024-10-20T04:39:00.578Z","_id":"cm2hd051800067oufgtl5hb53","layout":"post","photos":[],"excerpt":"","path":"2024/09/17/Coding-Problems/","permalink":"https://zweireverberate.icu/2024/09/17/Coding-Problems/","__post":true},"__post":true}